title: Looking to start a James Cook University club based in Townsville.
body:
I discovered recently that JCU does indeed have a club known as JCULOL however it's based up in Cairns. I will be beginning my first year and Uni this year and would be delighted to make some new friends. If anyone is interested be free to say so and I will contact you. 
{{sticker:slayer-pantheon-thumbs}}

replies.body: I was trying to track it down also.. I remember friends telling me about a LoL club, however this was 2 years ago. Check the Co-op bookshop, apparently the advertisements for clubs are posted on there.
Be sure to [register your uni club here](http://oce.leagueoflegends.com/en/featured/uni-clubs/register) :)
